children.name: Rules
children.text:
A small tin filled with viscous green slime, which slowly refills over time. Once per day, you can spend 10 minutes to apply the slime to a willing creature. The creature gains the following benefits for 8 hours:
- You have resistance to acid damage.
- Creatures have disadvantage to grapple you, and you have advantage on checks to escape from grapples or restraints.
